public static class UniprotJapiCallable.QueryEntryByIdCaller
extends Object
implements Callable<uk.ac.ebi.ep.search.model.EnzymeSummary>

A caller that implements the Callable interface that can be called to perform concurrent queries to Uniprot API to get Uniprot entries grouped by species. Actually, this callable is querying for species, getting the first one and using the first UniProt accession of it.
